'''熱帶爪蟾'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Xenopus tropicalis}}''）是[[負子蟾科|負子蟾科]]下的一種[[青蛙|青蛙]]。牠們是[[爪蟾屬|爪蟾屬]]下唯一擁有二倍體[[基因組|基因組]]的<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Enrique Amaya, Martin F. Offield, and Robert M. Grainger|title=Frog genetics: ''Xenopus tropicalis'' jumps into the future|journal=Trends in Genetics|volume=14|issue=7|date=1998-07-01|pages=253-5}}</ref>，且已被[[DNA序列|DNA序列]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://genome.jgi-psf.org/Xentr4/Xentr4.home.html |title=JGI X. tropicalis v4.1 |accessdate=2009-09-14 |archive-date=2012-10-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BUNi9UBt?url=http://genome.jgi-psf.org/Xentr4/Xentr4.home.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，補充了[[非洲爪蟾|非洲爪蟾]]成為[[遺傳學|遺傳學]]上的[[模式生物|模式生物]]。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Bowes ''et al.''|year=2008|url=http://nar.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/36/suppl_1/D761|title=Xenbase: a ''Xenopus'' biology and genomics resource|journal=Nucleic Acids Res|volume=36|pages=D761|access-date=2009-09-14|archive-date=2008-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080725220852/http://nar.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/36/suppl_1/D761|dead-url=no}}</ref>

